{"tid":2072774,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"以正視聽！重點不在國安法條文，而在立法過程的正當性！","createTime":"2020-06-20T23:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T07:50:00.000Z","uid":132265,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"949cff0988ecb93ffcef184fb6e3acd7d6fa64d3","tid":2072774,"uid":132265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T23:08:28.000Z","msg":"各位，睇個啲條文根本係浪費人生，好簡單一個例子，中國嘅憲法劈頭夠話保障宗教自由，但係事實邊度有過？呢啲例子多到喊，根本唔會有人相信中共！<br />\n<br />\n重點係，港區人大係咩機構？代表緊邊個？認受性黎自邊度？就好似當年831框架，香港人有得say咩？點解要我哋跟？乖乖哋坐低同你傾，然後呢？<br />\n<br />\n係一章削弱人權的法律，同你講保障人權，只係笑話一則。"},{"pid":"1338f5ee3ed3f88cd6ccbb1063fb3205f0c97401","tid":2072774,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T00:13:33.000Z","msg":"中聯辦話你知點樣 唔明顯咁封殺敏感書 (三中商）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2072788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2072788</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9fe3b1dc8ed60eb9bf1295f533efc4302b6a0e86","tid":2072774,"uid":63543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T00:39:05.000Z","msg":"why not both"},{"pid":"f0c6f0e773fcdf071834e84cef82f41953433386","tid":2072774,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fe3b1dc8ed60eb9bf1295f533efc4302b6a0e86","tid":2072774,"uid":63543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T00:39:05.000Z","msg":"why not both"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T00:41:02.000Z","msg":"Agree, both"},{"pid":"8bea1c001a4819b6c9f6de87445ce2ad332ca53d","tid":2072774,"uid":298213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T07:50:00.000Z","msg":"正當性?邊個有槍邊個就正當"}]}